snippet.title: Escape From Violet Institute - Final Trailer
snippet.description:
With this I say goodbye to working on this passion project, I had a lot of fun and learned a lot!
I can't wait to start my next one!

Escape From Violet Institute can be found here:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1265070/Escape_From_Violet_Institute/
